:::{{DIcon|Talk}} What is Janus' Steed?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504047042-->
::::'''Janus' Steed:''' Ever since Janus carved the boundary between heaven and earth, we have been there serving by their side. If Janus is the holiest "Gate of Infinity," then we are the physical "gates" &mdash; We open the way for them and pass on the prophecies.
::::'''Janus' Steed:''' There are endless types of "gates" out there, with some connecting areas, some linking spacetime, some separating inside from outside, and some... Just need one small key to deliver a big surprise.
::::'''Janus' Steed:''' "Gates" are connections. You and I meeting here is also a connection and a bond. Do you understand?
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} Your companions?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504047046-->
::::'''Janus' Steed:''' As time passes, the sentience of a divine foal will gradually erode. Or it may be misled and get lost in an endless journey. Or perhaps it might vanish completely, becoming a husk of its former self.
::::'''Janus' Steed:''' It's been an age since we separated, and I saw them last. O, divine foals... Am I really the only one left?
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} Why do you need Memory Crystal Shards?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504047049-->
::::'''Janus' Steed:''' Hmph, Oronyx and Janus have always been inseparable. Memories are connected through time and coexist spatially in space. Those shards contain authority beyond your wildest imagination.
::::'''Janus' Steed:''' As for the reason behind collecting all these... When the time comes, Janus will let you know.
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Return}} I don't have any more questions.
